  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "The proliferation of technology and internet connectivity in Thailand has created dominant super-app companies such as Grab (Deloitte, 2022).",
    "These companies have capitalized on their extensive networks to provide efficient same-day delivery services for e-commerce products.",
    "The immediate threat of obsolescence for logistics organizations that stick to traditional methods and disregard the adoption of digital transformation initiatives is primarily due to fierce market competition.",
    "The emergence of superapp giants in the Thai market highlights the imperative for conventional logistics companies to adjust and respond accordingly (Deloitte, 2022).",
    "Individuals need to adapt to this trend to maintain competitiveness, as the growing preference for digital platforms among customers for their shopping requirements could hinder their capacity to compete effectively."
  ],
